'''Sanasiki''' was a being who lived some time before the [[Jedi Civil War]] who killed a [[Zabrak/Legends|Zabrak]] [[Assassin/Legends|assassin]] named [[Nelinik]]. Some time afterwards, Sanasiki's personal blade fell into the possession of [[Crattis Yurkal]], and may have then been purchased from him by [[Revan/Legends|Revan]].<ref name="KOTOR">''[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic]]''</ref>

